name: bs-puppeteer
description: Bucklescript bindings for Puppeteer (headless chrome browser) written in Reason
author: Zach Ploskey <zach@ploskey.com>

scripts.snap: bsb -clean-world -make-world && rm -rf snap/* && mkdir -p snap && cp -ar lib/js snap/
scripts.snap-diff: bsb -clean-world -make-world && git diff --no-index snap/js lib/js || true
